Remarks
 FINANCIAL PERFORMANCE: F-15 EPAWSS is evaluated against traditional Research and Development (R&D) program expenditure benchmarks. Unlike many traditional
 R&D programs, however, the F-15 EPAWSS Development contract is a Fixed Price contract with progress payments. 10 percent of incurred costs are withheld until the end
 of the contract, when they are liquidated. Mandatory funding obligations and progress payment withholds will cause the program to lag traditional expenditure benchmarks,
 painting an inaccurate portrait of overall program health.




