Continue the RAM "Performance Lab" to provide quick turnaround raid performance curves which guide
integration, tactics, and future investments decisions. Continue to conduct experiments to verify the modeling
and simulation indicating performance improvements are grounded in actual testing. The major effort is analysis
of Red Sea engagements to inform software improvements conducted in the RAM Software Factory.

Continue Software (SW) Factory efforts to deliver missile software performance updates. The first major
software update (SW 7.09) was released in December 2024, and the second major update (SW 7.10) is on track
to deliver in October 2025.

