D. Acquisition Strategy
The SBIR acquisition process seeks to match projects with DLA’s Strategic Focus Areas. The goal is to align SBIR/STTR developed technology with current and future
DLA requirements. DLA solicits all new project execution work through the DOD SBIR Broad Agency Announcement (BAA). There are three separate solicitation
periods throughout each year. (Jan-Feb, May-Jun, and Sep-Oct)




