Description: This system improvement program (SIP) focuses on maintaining and upgrading capability and includes
development, integration, and testing and will continue to enhance missile survivability through subsystem updates, including
cyber security implementation and future flight demonstrations, such as the AGM-158XR. The SIP will explore and exploit new
form, fit, function hardware to maximize missile performance and address newly matured capabilities and emerging threats.
